 by clumps, with major contribution given by small clumps.\nThe enhancement due to large clumps with M>10^6 Msun is very small.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Dec 2004 17:23:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
