low current\nexperimental limits. The corrections to the hydrogen spectrum are expected to\nbe small but possibly detectable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Dec 2004 13:32:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Dec 2004 08:06:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 10 Apr 2006 13:32:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-17"}
